Eastern Platinum May Take Action Against Employees on Unlawful Strike

-- B y   A g n e s   N i k o i
-- 
2011-05-12T06:48:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-12/eastern-platinum-may-take-action-against-employees-on-unlawful-strike.html
Eastern Platinum Ltd. (ELR)  said ongoing
further unprotected industrial action, including an unlawful
blockade at the entrance of its Crocodile River Mine, may
require the commencement of legal action from today, according
to a statement on SEN newswire.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Agnes Nikoi at 
 anikoi@bloomberg.net  